# Committed test fixtures are real .pptx files (foreign-producer, not
# pptxgo's own output) despite the blanket *.pptx ignore above, which exists
# for generated demo/example output, not source-controlled test data.
!opc/testdata/*.pptx
!pptx/testdata/*.pptx
!examples/02_read_and_modify/template.pptx
